Atmeage Overview:

Activity focused on documenting data lineage for movement from GOPP to SDR.


Key Benefits:

Enhances traceability by linking data back to upstream systems in GOPP.

Enables tracking of end-to-end lineage for specific systems.

Verifies data accuracy and integrity.


Core Features:

Facilitates attestation of NFRs (Non-Functional Requirements).

Supports compliance with regulatory requirements and audit trails.

Aids in error identification and rectification.


Business Impact:

Builds trust and transparency in reporting processes.

Strengthens data reliability, supporting data-driven decision-making.



